        "product_description": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "These small glass vials with screw cap come case packed with 144 pieces in each vial set. They are ideal for storing liquids with their water tight screw on plastic cap or storing small items like beads, glitter, dust and other essential craft and hobby items. They will perform well in all laboratory conditions and are manufactured to the high quality standards to ensure they will work as expected each time without fail.<br/><br/>These small dram vials are made from Borosilicate glass, which is a type of glass that will not crack under extreme temperature changes like regular glass. Its durability has made it the glass of choice for laboratories, scientists, prospectors and collectors alike.<br/><br/>In addition to the glass body tube, the caps them selves which screw on are made from a thermoset plastic material known for its physical and molding properties. These caps show strength and durability with heat-resistant and insulating properties that are widely used in laboratory environments. Excellent resistance to corrosion and low moisture absorption. Making these lab sample vials able to be used with an autoclave. <br/><br/>These are the vials you want whether it is working in a laboratory or at home with your hobby and crafts, essential oils, beading or glitter. They perform the job without fail.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
